二、指定教科書及參考資料 Textbooks and Reference(請修課同學遵守智慧財產權，不得非法影印)


●指定教科書 Required Texts無
		●參考書資料暨網路資源 Reference Books and Online ResourcesAntitrust Enforcement & IPR - Promoting Innovation & Competition, issued by the U.S. Department of Justice & the Federal Trade Commission (Apr 2007)Antitrust Guidelines for Collaborations Among Competitors, issued by the U.S. Department of Justice & the Federal Trade Commission (Apr 2000)


三、教學目標 Objectives


藉由研讀部分教材及實務書狀引導在職學生瞭解反托拉斯法、如何遵循相關法規，及實務措施以減少觸犯。　


四、課程內容 Course Description


●整體敘述 Overall Description本學期擬涵蓋下列主題：Horizontal Relationships (Horizontal Price-Fixing; Buyer Cartels; Horizontal Output Restrictions; Horizontal Market Divisions; Boycott)Unilateral Conduct (Conduct elements; Predatory Pricing; Excessive Pricing; Unilateral Refusal to Deal; Predatory Buying; Price Squeezes)Vertical Relationships (Intro; Exclusive Dealing; Tying-in; Resale Price Maintenance; Loyalty & Bundling Discounts; Vertical Restraints; Vertical Non-Price restraints; Vertical Maximum Price-fixing; Vertical Minimum Price-fixing; Dual Distribution Issues; Price Discrimination; Proving an Agreement or a Concerted Action)Mergers (Horizontal Mergers; Vertical Mergers; Conglomerate Mergers)Enforcement : Dept of Justice (criminal proceedings); Private suits (statute of limitation & antitrust injury)


●分週敘述 Weekly Schedule





